text: Vitaly Sapronov (Russian: Виталий Сапронов; born 17 June 1945) is a Soviet rower. He competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics in Munich with the men's coxless four where they came in fourth place. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1972 Summer Olympics
